highlighted phrase: closest structural homologues a structural homology search using the dali server reveals that , overall , our structure is most similar to structures of bacterial ftsh ( thermotoga maritima , 2cea , 2ce7 ; helicobacter pylori , 2r65 ; t. thermophilus , 2dhr , 1iy0 ; escherichia coli , 1lv7 ) , p97 / vcp ( in particular the d2 subunit ; 3cf0 ) , human fidgetin - like protein - 1 ( 3d8b ) and the human vps4 / skd1 atpase ( 1xwi ) .
